defs.name: StreamerError
defs.value:
pub enum StreamerError {

    #[error("I/O error")]
    Io(
       #[from]
       std::io::Error),

    #[error("receive timeout error")]
    RecvTimeoutError(
                     #[from]
                     RecvTimeoutError),

    #[error("send packets error")]
    SendError(
              #[from]
              SendError<Packets>),
}
